('alness', 'Alness', 'https://www.alnessgolf.co.uk/Teebooking/SearchSlots.aspx', 'https://www.alnessgolf.co.uk/Teebooking/SearchSlots.aspx', 'Yes', 'No', 'dotgolf', 'dotgolf', '', 'highlands', 'Yes', 57.704756, -4.264156, 0, 2018, '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 0, 'd', 0xe61000000101000000302b14e97e0e11c074d4d17135da4c40, 'nonlinks', 'No', 'Alness Golf Club, located in the Scottish Highlands, offers a charming and challenging parkland layout. The course features gently rolling fairways, mature trees, and well-protected greens that reward careful approaches. Its scenic location provides stunning views of the surrounding hills, rivers, and countryside, creating an immersive Highland experience for players of all abilities.\r\n\r\nWhile approachable for beginners, Alness provides subtle challenges for more experienced golfers. Undulating fairways and strategically placed hazards encourage thoughtful shot-making, requiring both accuracy and creativity. The club balances a relaxed, welcoming atmosphere with the strategic demands of the course, creating an environment where players can enjoy golf at their own pace.\r\n\r\nThe Highland setting adds a sense of remoteness and tranquility, allowing golfers to connect with the natural beauty of Scotland. Alness Golf Club is highly regarded for its friendly community, scenic appeal, and enjoyable layout. Its combination of challenge, accessibility, and picturesque surroundings makes it a memorable destination for visitors and locals alike, delivering a classic Scottish golfing experience.', ''),
