('ardeer', 'Ardeer', 'https://ardeergolfclub.co.uk/', 'https://ardeergolfclub.co.uk/', 'No', 'No', '', '', '', 'ayrshire', '', 55.654460, -4.748280, 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 0, 'd', 0xe61000000101000000e700c11c3dfe12c024456458c5d34b40, 'nonlinks', 'No', 'Ardeer Golf Club, located in North Ayrshire, is a classic seaside links course that challenges players with firm fairways, coastal winds, and strategically placed bunkers. The layout blends traditional Scottish links design with natural dunes, making accuracy and careful club selection essential. While approachable for casual golfers, it provides a true test of links golf for experienced players.\r\n\r\nSeveral holes run close to the coast, offering stunning sea views and exposure to the elements, which adds both challenge and visual appeal. The course combines shorter par threes with longer holes that reward strategic thinking and precise shot execution.\r\n\r\nArdeer is known for its friendly, community-focused atmosphere, providing a welcoming environment for visitors. Its combination of classic links design, coastal scenery, and approachable challenge ensures a memorable golfing experience. Golfers enjoy the authentic Scottish links character, where every round feels both competitive and scenic.', ''),
